headline: Is There Still Value Left in Carnival Stock After Its 227% Three Year Surge?
summary: If you have been wondering whether Carnival Corporation & is still a bargain after its big recovery story, you are not alone. Investors are trying to figure out if there is more value left in the tank or if the easy gains are over. The stock has climbed 6.8% over the last week, 6.1% over the past month and is up 10.4% year to date, adding to a remarkable 226.9% gain over 3 years, even though the 1 year return sits at a more modest 6.6%.
